verbose_text: Sequential exposure to IL-15 and TGF-beta, shown to optimally induce de novo CD8 + CD69 + CD103 + T RM cells from PBMCs was also able to efficiently upregulate autophagy, with the latter effect attributable to IL-15 (XREF_FIG A and 5B).
evidence: RM  cells from PBMCs               was also able to efficiently upregulate autophagy
